<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-026-112 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 452 212</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  Oct 29 1991 v5 n37 p6(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Now scheduler lets workgroups keep their calendars Up-To-Date;program allows remote updating. (Now Software Inc.'s NowUp-To-Date multiuser calendar and scheduling software package)(product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Brown, Dartanyan.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Now Software Inc. (Product introduction).andO;Product:   Now Up-To-Date (Computer program) (Product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionSchedulingCalendarsSoftware PackagesMultiuser SoftwareWork Group Computing.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Program allows remote updatingandM;By Dartanyan BrownandM;Portland, Ore.andP;  -- Now Software Inc. has a way for users on the road or inthe office to keep their workgroup's shared calendar up-to-date.andM;Called Now Up-To-Date, the multi-user calendar and scheduling program letsusers create and share calendar files over AppleTalk networks, either locallyor via remote dial-up access, the company said.andM;To ship in December, Now Up-To-Date uses a proprietary technology that allowsusers to disseminate calendar information to other workgroup members atregular intervals.andP;  Shared calendars record the name of the last person tomake changes to them.andM;All shared calendars reside on one Mac with the Now Up-To-Date extensioninstalled.andP;  Any workstation on the network can be the server; there is noadministration software.andM;While users can create private calendars, individual calendar events can bemade public, allowing them to be shared with members of the workgroup.andM;Password protection allows either view-and-edit capability or view-onlyaccess.andM;Now Up-To-Date includes event information, such as title, date and duration.andO;The program offers daily, weekly and monthly views; audio alarms forscheduled events; electronic Post-it notes; and printing options that supportmost popular appointment-book formats.andM;Text, style and graphic attributes can be customized for each calendar.andO;Custom views including information from multiple calendars retain thoseattributes.andM;Now Up-To-Date will sell for $99 per single user.andP;  Five-user packs will be$399; 10-user packs will be $599.andM;Now Software Inc. is at 520 S.W.andP;  Harrison, Suite 435, Portland, Ore.andP;  97201.andO;Phone (503) 274-2800; fax (503) 274-0670.andO;</TEXT></DOC>